to;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And the girl also showed where her house was, so that next time the animal would have somewhere to wait out the bad weather.  The cat took advantage of this, but already took the whole family with her.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ofGQUlN</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Thryloz]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>For my 37th birthday I decided to start taking care of myself. Six months progress</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/0TxLYBU</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ECcmi85.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I got a desk job seven years ago and slowly started putting on weight due to some depression, drinking too much and lack of exercise.  I decided to get serious about my health around the first week of December. I haven’t been perfect but I think I’ve done pretty well. I’ve always had some self image problems but I felt pretty good today.  #progress_pic #progress</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/0TxLYBU</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ChrisE13579]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>old timey life hacks</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/IEtnUHC</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KVyX0N9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WHHDGSl.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pX8mnfQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XnhJYtm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SSVRmHq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KToVLtV.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>