9dwXJ.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>A friend is a friend.  Friends don't see your flaws.  Friends don't care about limits, they only care that you're included in their lives.  

Be a friend to someone.  The world needs more friends, I think.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/NqutzTT</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MayMyEnemiesLiveLong]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Top tier joke</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Fyg5rlN</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2qSzb5D.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>If you like it then go ahead and send knudes.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Fyg5rlN</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[HelloThere1812]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I'm confused. Litigation department for Tesla to initiate and execute lawsuits? Someone 'splain it to me.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/0lahLH7</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/h2OxrD4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/0lahLH7</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[funkystay]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>This will be the last time I refer to him as my 'brother'</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/JRPtjX9</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GmTu7Dh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is simply a means for catharsis so I thank you for being an avenue I can take without doing harm to people who do not want the exposure (victims).

Story time. MANY years ago my brother molested me at the age of 8 or so, I kept this a secret for decades, in all honesty I lied to myself and ALMOST convinced myself it never happened, or that it was somehow my own misunderstanding of the events that took place (ridiculous). I went to therapy years later but at the time my drug and alcohol addiction were beginning to run rampant so there was little hope for therapy helping. I learned to just stuff it along with other trauma I was dealing with. Eventually I got sober, changed my life, came to terms with things that had happened and was slammed back to reality this last summer when my sister (who had been randomly triggered by something in her life) suddenly remembered that she too had been molested by him. HOLY SHIT. The grief, the pain, the validation. It wrecked us both. We cut him out of our lives but our parents don't know how to handle this news and just attempt to hold the family together while honoring our wishes to not want to see him. They include him in group texts with us and that's pushing it, especially for my sister because this wound is very fresh. But mostly, we learn to deal. 

Fast forward to now, my grandmother is on her death bed and I have started reaching out to a cousin with whom I've kind of lost connection with.  We've shared a lot of similar difficulties with addiction and whatnot and we've always been the black sheep of our respective families. In speaking about how our lives are going the focus shifts to siblings and how we get along with each other now. I explain the rift in my own family, that some memories of a family member suddenly became flashbacks of molestation and he says 'I share the same memories.' 

Fuck. Simultaneous feelings of further validation and outright disgust as I realize that what I've CONVINCED myself was just a curious teenage brother's perverted stupidity (I know, I know, it's so much more) became predator behavior. I have started wondering at what point to do I start contacting my childhood friends and asking them if my brother ever did anything to them. 

TLDR I found out there's a trail of family members that my brother has molested and he's a stupid piece of shit. My hatred for him over the last 20 so years is completely and totally justified, I have no brother.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/JRPtjX9</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Thlsisjustatribute]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>When you bond with your buddy’s dog at a party and someone else walks over trying to hop in.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/TXXW8q1</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/e7zmEUA.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Fun stuff.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/TXXW8q1</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[deafkitten]]></dc:creator></item></channel></rss>